docs.text: Grokking Algorithms First Chapter def binary_search(l: typing.List[], e: int): start = 0 end = len(l) - 1 mid = (end - start) // 2 while True: if e == mid: break if e < mid: high = mid if e > mid: start = mid mid = (end - start) // 2
